item.title: Cant Run Client or Log Into Any Servers
item.dc:creator: @legend-scape legend-scape
item.description:
@legend-scape wrote:

Jared77:

Well, I havent been into servers for a while, and I wanted to start playing again. Since then I got a new computer, so I am wondering if I am missing something. I have Java and WinRAR installed. But every client i try to download it wont let me. I download it and every time i get “exception in thread…” for at least 10 servers. I finally got Silab v4 to work but i cant log into any servers, I always get “Error connecting…” for at least 25 servers, even ones with 100% uptime. Anyone know whats wrong?

well to get on server with a client goto your server file’s then goto client.java then search for the ip of the client and then change it to what server u wont to go on E.G 123654865.no-ip.org or . biz/info,
